infra.description: ZYNQ-7S ZYNQ-7S TE0722-*-07S-1C (0GB DDR) Board (form factor 1.8 x 5.1 cm) with single ARM Cortex-A9, without DDR, speed grade -1 and commercial temperature range. *Supported PCB Revisions: REV02.
